Result-mapping changes:

```typescript
return {
  // existing fields...
  workflow: opts.workflow,                                    // string | true | undefined
  withWorkflowAgents: opts.workflowAgents !== false,          // default true
  workflowAttach: opts.workflowAttach !== false,              // default true
  workflowPane: Boolean(opts.workflowPane),                   // default false
