| New agent-*.jsonl appearance attaches dynamically | start with 0 agents, then write agent file | wait ~200ms | onOutput called with agent label |
| Duplicate dir-watch event for same agent file deduped | start with 0 agents, write same file twice | wait | attachAgent called only once |
