End-to-end check using temp dir fixture: write journal + 2 agent jsonls + snapshot, dispatch, verify output buffer contents.

## Critical Files for Implementation

- `src/claude-workflow/workflow-detector.ts` — NEW; path B dir watch
- `src/claude-workflow/watch-builder.ts` — NEW; WorkflowAttachment + label helpers
