## Acceptance Mapping

| ID | Requirement | P3 coverage |
|----|-------------|-------------|
| T4 | `--workflow <runId>` shows journal + existing agents | startClaudeWorkflowMultiWatch + WorkflowAttachment initial scan |
| T5 | New journal line shown within 1s | journal FileWatcher follow mode (existing tail logic) |
| T6 | New agent transcript attached within 1s | subagentDirWatcher → attachAgent |
| T7 | `--no-workflow-agents` skips agents | `withAgents: false` in WorkflowAttachment config |

## Out of P3 scope

